Declare: used to declaring the varibales.
syntax: 
 declare <var> "$ABAP.TYPE( S_CARR_ID );
         here S_CARR_ID --> is the data element; 
              once assign the data element it is sending the chracteristics to the <var>.
              
declare internal table:
  DECLARE mytab table( mandt  "$ABAP.type( mandt )",
                       uname  "$ABAP.type( syst_uname )",
                       langu  "$ABAP.type( syst_langu )",
                       datum  "$ABAP.type( syst_datum )",
                       text   "$ABAP.type( line-text )",
                       number "$ABAP.type( f )" );

